edu.harvard.cga.gtools.tekml
Class KmlTimeData

java.lang.Object
  edu.harvard.cga.gtools.tekml.KmlTimeData

public class KmlTimeData
extends java.lang.Object

A simple data transport object containing KML time data The data elements are Strings expected to conform to ISO8601 Both timespan (a pair of values) and timestamp (a single value) are supported by the same class.

Author:
W.Hays (whays at nearity.com)
